                                                                 Proxy (filter in servlet) (Broker)
                                                                 
             - It is extra layer added
             - pre-checking the request
             
             
             
                          Client ----------->        Proxy  ----------->      Real Object      
                          
            - Proxy is used to pre checking the request 
            - checking log, data(Validation) 
            - This is achieve by Inheritance by extends the class create object for child child class check the data and call the parent class(which is server Original class)
            
            
